      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "That logic is incredibly tempting when the weight of existence feels unbearable, but your life holds value that extends beyond just your immediate impact on others. Even if it feels like you are taking up space, your presence can still offer comfort, inspiration, or simply be a beautiful memory to those who love you. Please consider speaking with a mental health professional who can help you navigate these feelings of emptiness and find a path that honors your life without needing to disappear.",
